# Backend API origin. Required in production when frontend and API are on different hosts (card images are served from API /uploads).
# Leave unset for same-origin (e.g. dev proxy or when reverse proxy serves both app and API under one domain).
# Example: https://your-api.railway.app
# VITE_API_URL=

# Optional: app icon/logo URL. Used in headers, nav, and QR code center. Fallback: /favicon.png
# Use absolute URL (https://...) or path (e.g. /logo.svg). For cross-origin, image must be CORS-enabled.
# VITE_APP_ICON_URL=
